  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the rugged, dystopian Wild West, where iron rails carve paths through vast forests, towering mountains, and treacherous canyons. As a determined engineer and a sharp-eyed gunner, you'll embark on a daring journey aboard a steam train, tasked with delivering vital supplies across lawless territories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your train is more than just a mode of transport; it's a lifeline for the frontier. The back cargo car brims with resupplyable ammo boxes and a formidable machine gun, ready to fend off relentless bandit attacks. The central cargo hold carries precious supplies that must reach their destination at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through stunning landscapes, from the dense beauty of forests and the imposing heights of mountains to the strategic checkpoints at the borders. Every stretch of track holds new challenges, from fierce shootouts with bandits to high-speed chases with outlaws in vehicles. Stay vigilant, protect your cargo, and ensure safe delivery to secure the future of the frontier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/7d50b8bfd767d1343f6e9a475c893d0b.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/7d50b8bfd767d1343f6e9a475c893d0b.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/7d50b8bfd767d1343f6e9a475c893d0b.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember, each delivery strengthens your country’s war effort. Are you ready for the challenge?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/60aca8dde06da3f0c380827a8b6571eb.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/60aca8dde06da3f0c380827a8b6571eb.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/60aca8dde06da3f0c380827a8b6571eb.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f00de3df6624d501c79824d662dfab0e.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f00de3df6624d501c79824d662dfab0e.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f00de3df6624d501c79824d662dfab0e.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ADD CUSTOM SONGS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add your favorite music to listen to on the train radio in the games folder location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f5f7aaee0cedbd91fa391f435fa323cf.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f5f7aaee0cedbd91fa391f435fa323cf.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/f5f7aaee0cedbd91fa391f435fa323cf.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the rugged, dystopian Wild West, where iron rails carve paths through vast forests, towering mountains, and treacherous canyons. As a determined engineer and a sharp-eyed gunner, you'll embark on a daring journey aboard a steam train, tasked with delivering vital supplies across lawless territories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.poster.avif?t=1733914183\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.webm?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2757400/extras/4c397ffaba232439b5fb6a33d190ba8a.mp4?t=1733914183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your train is more than just a mode of transport; it's a lifeline for the frontier. The back cargo car brims with resupplyable ammo boxes and a formidable machine gun, ready to fend off relentless bandit attacks. The central cargo hold carries precious supplies that must reach their destination at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through stunning landscapes, from the dense beauty of forests and the imposing heights of mountains to the strategic checkpoints at the borders. Every stretch of track holds new challenges, from fierce shootouts with bandits to high-speed chases with outlaws in vehicles. Stay vigilant, protect your cargo, and ensure safe delivery to secure the future of the frontier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steam